    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and she\u2019s looking for a new home! This car has been absolutely wonderful to me\u2014super reliable and a total joy to drive. It\u2019s been well-loved and well-maintained, so it\u2019s in great shape and ready for your next road trip or daily commute. You\u2019re going to love how smooth it feels on the road. Drop me a message if you want to come see it!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
